title: 031 - Which Type Of Aliens Are Superior?
description: On today's show, Tony gives his delayed review of the Netflix phenomenon sweeping the globe, Extraction. The boys also chat about Connor going to high school for 5 years, Tony breaking in his $200 roller blades, Chuck E. Cheese rebranding as Pasquale's in order to let their kitchens stand alone, and what type of movie alien would be the most formidable if they were to attack earth. Make sure to keep sending your questions into @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram, and as always, stay safe out there. Enjoy.
